1.0.name: wordpress/edgeio-classifieds
1.0.description:
Add your own paid or free classifieds to your word press blog, completely configurable. Many samples available. Works with MU as well.

/* *Edgeio for Wordpress Plugin v1.0 ReadMe *Adds your own Classsifieds board to Wordpress site. *Prepopulating with live data from Edgeio classiofieds yet allowing your users to post own paid and free classifieds *Requires Wordpress 2+ or Wordpress MU *@license http://opensource.org/licenses/gpl-license.php GNU Public License *@ by Andrew Yasinsky andrew@edgeio.com *home page http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/edgeio-classifieds/ **/

Basic Installation

The plug in can be configured as complex or as simple as you wish.

Important edgeio_plugin.php is for generic php installations if you have word press delete it and use wp_edgeio
